  <section id="production">
    <title>
      Our facilities
    </title>

    <p>
      The SFM production premises were purpose-built in 2015.  They are
      located in the industrial center of Jelgava, just 45&space;km from
      Riga.
    </p>

    <p>
      The 3500&space;m² area has a maximum lift capacity of 30 tonnes.
      Our facilities for shotblasting and spray painting are among the
      largest and most modern in the country.  We also have a final
      assembly area.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our facilities are highly capable. We can do:
    </p>

    <compact-list>
      <item>
        MIG/MAG welding
      </item>
      <item>
        TIG welding
      </item>
      <item>
        rolling
      </item>
      <item>
        turning
      </item>
      <item>
        sawing
      </item>
      <item>
        shotblasting
      </item>
      <item>
        wet painting
      </item>
      <item>
        cold zinc spraying
      </item>
      <item>
        pneumatic tapping
      </item>
      <item>
        plasma cutting
      </item>
      <item>
        advanced measuring
      </item>
      <item>
        electrical wiring
      </item>
      <item>
        semi- and final assembly
      </item>
    </compact-list>

